{"tid":2254897,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［人唔笑］美酒佳餚巡禮線上舉行 旅發局主席：畀海外旅客知道香港市民生活如常","createTime":"2020-10-23T07:15:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-23T07:51:53.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"bd6dac4596893e5d407b760a29e574cce1b4926b","tid":2254897,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T07:15:58.000Z","msg":"（獨媒報導）因應疫情，「香港美酒佳餚巡禮」將於11月11日至12月15日改於網上舉行，市民可上網訂購外賣、食材、酒精飲料，及出席網上課程學習烹飪品酒。旅遊發展局主席彭耀佳認為，舉辦網上巡禮除可推動本地經濟外，亦能重新接觸海外旅客，「畀佢哋知道香港市民生活如常」，吸引往後來港消費。商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華表示支持，「線上線下都可以做（旅遊）」，指「就算去旅行，未去之前都會線上睇好多資料」。<br />\n<strong><br />\n是次網上「香港美酒佳餚巡禮」將有逾100間酒商參與，超過500間餐廳提供優惠及外賣套餐，</strong>以及34堂免費網上大師班。彭耀佳指，市民除可透過一站式網站平台訂購美食送貨上門，亦可獲得許多盛名的大師傳授深入的心得，「唔係普通網購嚟㗎」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1078374\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1078374&d=LL0CSI02xgrrxVkOh%2Fu%2FRFR4K0ufT%2FFGu3kbIPb6xA8%3D&h=ef4b2210\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1078374&h=662a5ea9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1078374</a><br />\n<br />\n賣食物定賣酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49c9b686f389373a7981fd80b2e16f6caf3ce296","tid":2254897,"uid":116289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T07:16:54.000Z","msg":"賣智商<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cfa4805180b03f4858430e8e599eeefb41b8eaf","tid":2254897,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T07:33:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e3aa9f11c81b38920d494cf20c07977e4705ad7b","tid":2254897,"uid":246828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T07:35:44.000Z","msg":"試酒係咪要舔個mon<img src=\"